## 🐛 Common Issues

| Problem | Fix |
|---|---|
| `port 8000 already in use` | Run `lsof -i :8000` and kill the process, or change the port in `docker-compose.yml` |
| `port 5173 already in use` | Change the port in `docker-compose.yml` and `vite.config.js` |
| DB connection error | Double-check `DATABASE_URL` in `.env`. Ensure Neon DB is active. |
| CORS error in browser | Backend allows all origins by default (`*`). Check the frontend API base URL. |
| `Module not found` (frontend) | Run `npm install` inside the `frontend/` folder |
| Docker build fails | Make sure Docker Desktop is running and try `docker-compose down --rmi all` then rebuild |

